传统强碱清洁剂温和，没有刺鼻化学味，对皮肤友好。去油效果快且不伤不锈钢表面，擦完锃亮锃亮的。5瓶家庭装实惠，用完会继续回购，支持国产好货！\\\"\\n\\n---\\n\\n**评论设计亮点**：  \\n1. 覆盖不同用户群体（主妇/租房党/性价比用户等）  \\n2. 结合产品核心卖点（去污力、容量、安全性）  \\n3. 使用具体场景描述增强真实感  \\n4. 包含价格对比和复购意愿提升可信度  \\n5. 平衡优点与轻微使用提醒（如戴手套）更显客观\", \"cos_fee\": 9.56, \"has_sxt\": true, \"is_redu\": 1, \"is_sole\": false, \"kol_num\": \"7.5w-10w\", \"shop_id\": \"435468\", \"up_time\": 1768800028, \"combined\": 66, \"end_time\": \"2026-02-28\", \"in_stock\": true, \"is_exist\": 1, \"platform\": \"douyin\", \"sales_24\": \"1w-2.5w\", \"sharable\": \"1\", \"view_num\": 1880163, \"cos_ratio\": 0.32, \"first_cid\": \"20115\", \"gift_info\": \"\", \"goods_url\": \"https://www.reduxingxuan.com/detail?id=157101\", \"is_sample\": 0, \"order_num\": \"10w-25w\", \"post_time\": \"\", \"rd_status\": 1, \"shop_logo\": \"https://p3-ecom-qualification-sign.ecombdimg.com/tos-cn-i-6vegkygxbk/e0bd13fcaa654b029df323ed47168bda~tplv-6vegkygxbk-s:750.image?lk3s=c9156bde&x-expires=1761803605&x-signature=cp9R17B71XD02BngomTuOOCAPuc%3D\", \"shop_name\": \"水卫士官方旗舰店\", \"skus_info\": {\"skus\": {\"1756635288285212\": {\"skuId\": 1756635288287324, \"stock_num\": 8182138, \"effective_price\": 2990}}, \"specs\": [{\"name\": \"清洁套餐\", \"spec_items\": [{\"id\": \"1756635288285212\", \"name\": \"买1发5瓶【重油污克星】\"}]}], \"pictures\": {\"1756635288285212\": {\"big_picture\": \"https://p3-item.ecombdimg.com/img/ecom-shop-material/LNbnnQT_m_b762058270f0d849ce49a52aaa638dcb_sx_510710_www800-800~tplv-5mmsx3fupr-resize:1200:0.webp\", \"little_picture\": \"https://p3-item.ecombdimg.com/img/ecom-shop-material/LNbnnQT_m_b762058270f0d849ce49a52aaa638dcb_sx_510710_www800-800~tplv-5mmsx3fupr-resize:300:0.webp\"}}}, \"third_cid\": 28601, \"begin_time\": \"2025-01-16\", \"brand_name\": \"水卫士\", \"butie_rate\": 0, \"order_week\": \"5w-7.5w\", \"pay_amount\": 0, \"post_place\": \"\", \"product_id\": \"3514626926616666110\", \"sales_7day\": \"5w-7.5w\", \"second_cid\": 21778, \"shop_goods\": [{\"id\": \"5472111\", \"url\": \"https://